When running Visual Studio 2022 with CmdLine@2 task, the task runs fine but does not detect that Visual Studio 2022 finished the work.
After 58 min, the task timeout, and job fails.
Is it related to the fact that Visual Studio 2022 is 64 bit app ?

I call this task to build a MSI based on a Microsoft Installer Project in the solution.
Microsoft Installer Project is in [windows-2022 env](https://github.com/actions/virtual-environments/issues/4580).

I experience the same issue with [DevEnvBuild](https://github.com/mmajcica/DevEnvBuild). Works with Visual Studio 2019, timeout with Visual Studio 2022.
